	<text xml:lang="la">
		<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" subtype="metadata" n="1">Daß der Brief an <persName ref="p8418" cert="high">Myconius</persName> gerichtet ist, ergibt sich aus dem Inhalt wie auch aus der Antwort vom 26. August (unten <ref target="file10926">Nr. 885</ref>).</note>
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">Gratiam et pacem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Vehementer doluit, frater in domino venerande, quod non licuit maiori vos prosequi benevolentia et humanitate<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Zum Besuch von <persName ref="p8418">Myconius</persName> und <persName ref="p1365">Grynäus</persName> in <placeName ref="l587">Zürich</placeName> s. oben <ref target="file10918">Nr. 877</ref>, 5-30.</note>; certe voluntas non defuit.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Nunc, quid <placeName ref="l41">Bernae</placeName> impetraveritis<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Vgl. den Bericht der <placeName ref="l41">Berner</placeName> Pfarrer über die Verhandlungen vom 17. August, oben <ref target="file10919">Nr. 878</ref>.</note>, scire cupimus.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Quid doctor <persName ref="p4079">Ioannes Zviccius</persName> a <placeName ref="l257">Constantia</placeName> scripserit<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Oben <ref target="file10920">Nr. 879</ref>.</note> hic habetis., Quodsi vestrates conventum cogere volunt generalem, consultissimum tum propter causam tum propter nos videtur, si post nundinas hoc agant <placeName ref="l157">Francfordianas</placeName><note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Die <placeName ref="l157">Frankfurter</placeName> Herbstmesse fand in der Regel zwischen Mariä Himmelfahrt (15. August) und Mariä Geburt (8. September) statt; s. Alexander <hi>Dietz,</hi> Frankfurter Handelsgeschichte, Bd. I, Frankfurt a. M. 1910, S. 37-40.</note>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Interim enim <persName ref="p8049">Vadiani</persName> libros recipiet <persName ref="p1974">Lutherus</persName><note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Vgl. oben <ref target="file10922">Nr. 881</ref>, 6f.</note> palamque, quid animo volvat, exponet.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Certe - ut libere, quod sentio, dicam - videtur unus <persName ref="p4079">Zviccius</persName> planius negotium hoc exposuisse quam <placeName ref="l491">Argentoratenses</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Expectamus a vobis responsionem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" ana="salute"><persName ref="p1365">Grynaeum</persName>, ecclesiarum decus, ex me salutabis diligentissime.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la">Huic communicabis perpetuo, quae scribo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Valebitis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la">24. Augusti 1536.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la">Tuus per omnia</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p495">H. Bullingerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Ohne Adresse.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
